cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software in research, please cite it as below."
title: "Health Agent Infra: A governed runtime for personal-health agents"
abstract: >-
  A local-first governance layer for personal-health agents. It combines
  deterministic policy, typed state ledgers, packaged skills, and a review
  loop so an LLM can help operate over health data without owning the rules,
  state, or commit path.
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Dom
    family-names: Colligan
repository-code: "https://github.com/dtcolligan/health_agent_infra"
url: "https://github.com/dtcolligan/health_agent_infra"
license: MIT
keywords:
  - personal-health
  - LLM-agents
  - runtime-enforcement
  - local-first
  - deterministic-policy
  - intervals.icu
  - garmin
  - claude-code
version: "0.1.8"
date-released: "2026-04-25"
